You must format and mount a drive here.

DO NOT attempt to use a local directory or the install
may overwrite your local system and render it un-bootable.

The following partitions are required in a gpt formatted drive:

type               size    Label            Mountpint
grub-bios          512k    none             none
fat32              100M    EFI-SYSTEM       rootfs/boot/efi
ext4               5G+     USB_ROOT         rootfs
swap               2G      USB_SWAP         none
btrfs             max      USB_DATA         none

